(5694, 178479, 'Kitsuné: The Witch (Feat. Sourya) EP', 'The talented French producer Dombrance is releasing “The Witch” in association with Sourya, one of the most exciting collaborationsemerging from the Parisien scene !  \r\nOut on Kitsuné – March 11th\r\n\r\nDombrance is a songwriter, singer, producer, remixer from Bordeaux. Before composing for himself, he has collaborated with a whole range of artists from Charlélie Coutureto DJ Chloé thanks to his production’s talents.\r\n\r\nHaving whittled 24 songs to a core of 2, Dombrance called singer Sou (Sourya) to add his elegant and soulful voice to the instrumental monster.The result is ''''The Witch'''', a brilliant single that holds a wealth of contained emotion and blissful dynamics and combines minimal with pop in a kinda soulful way. \r\n\r\n“The Witch”, which was one of the highlights of the Gildas Club Night Mix 3 out last December, is backed for this release by 4 exclusive remixes by the dancey “David Shaw and the beat remix” , the dark “Enola remix”, the brilliant French electro-pop band “Aswefall”, and the rising djs of “The Access”. \r\n\r\nAn opposition of styles makes this new EP brilliant and one of the most expected Kitsuné release of this early year! \r\n\r\nTracklisting\r\n---------------------------------------\r\n1.	Original mix \r\n2.	David Shaw and The Beat remix \r\n3.	Aswefall remix\r\n4.	Enola remix\r\n5.	The Acces remix\r\n\r\nhttps://www.facebook.com/dombrance\r\nwww.kitsune.fr\r\n', '2013-03-11 00:00:00', 0, 2, 3, '', 'Kitsuné', 0, '', 0, 0, '2013-03-20 12:05:06', '2015-02-16 15:48:50', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(5695, 91495, '美麗的夜晚/Beautiful Night', '科技讓我們低頭 常常忘了仰望\r\n情緒讓我們失衡 常常忘了溫柔\r\n渴望讓我們急切 常常忘了等候\r\n失序在生活裡展開\r\n其實回到最初的原點\r\n看見平安一直在那兒\r\n感受力量不斷充滿\r\n就算飛到海極之處\r\n祂的慈愛始終環繞不斷絕', '2012-11-22 00:00:00', 0, 1, 18, 'Yvonne Victoria Karlsson', 'FireMakers', 0, '', 1, 0, '2013-03-20 16:35:13', '2015-02-16 15:48:50', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(5696, 91495, '馬槽裡的榮耀/The Glory of the Manger', '他的『琴』，贏得世人肯定，獲獎無數\r\n他的『心』，想領你與亙古守候的愛相遇\r\n他的『愛』，想與你分享遇見生命的夢奇地\r\n\r\n發行這張專輯是嘉健生命意外之旅，驚喜上帝帶自己\r\n去到二千多年前的馬槽裡，聽見鋼琴外的聲音， 很確\r\n定聽到的是：“Gloria, in excelsis Deo”！--至高者的榮耀！\r\n回想來台這些年上帝所予點滴，很清楚必須把這句話編入\r\n聖誕古曲裏成為隱藏之主題…\r\n\r\n期待每個人聆聽時， 也能聽見天使佳音：\r\n“在至高之處榮耀歸與 神，在地上平安歸與祂所喜悅的人。”', '2012-11-22 00:00:00', 0, 1, 13, '周嘉健', 'FireMakers', 0, '', 1, 0, '2013-03-22 14:50:19', '2015-02-16 15:48:50', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
