(5724, 156879, '濃情四重奏電影原聲帶', '濃情四重奏電影原聲帶\nA Late Quartet O.S.T.\n編號3718829 條碼02537188291\n由奧斯卡最佳男配角克里斯多佛華肯和奧斯卡影帝菲利浦西摩霍夫曼同台飆戲的《濃情四重奏》，描述領導四重奏的大提琴手彼特，在樂團25週年公演前，發現自己罹患了帕金森氏症，他逐漸顫抖的雙手開始握不緊琴弓，而團體四人多年來累積在心頭的愛恨情仇又在此時爆發，原本關係親密的四重奏瀕臨崩解，他們是否能及時夠敞開心房，重新奏出震撼人心的天籟之音？本片原創配樂請來大師級的Angelo Badalamenti擔綱，作為大導大衛林區的御用作曲家，向來奇詭淒美的招牌曲風，此次卻譜出滄桑中帶著暖意的樂章，而貫穿全片的貝多芬: 升C小調第14號弦樂四重奏，則選用由Brentano四重奏演出的版本，與原創配樂完美融合，帶出藝術家豐沛情感的人生意境！\n\n1.A Late Quartet Overture\n2.Movements\n3.Diagnosis\n4.Reflections\n5.A Jog in the Park\n6.Stop Right Here\n7.11:42PM\n8.Premonition\n9.Winter Love\n10.Eternal Quest\n11.Old Men Know\n12.Breaking Up\n13.Fire Escape\n14.Longing for Miriam\n15.A Late Quartet Bidding Farewell\n16.Korngold: Gluck, das mir verblieb\n17.Bulerias Del Encuentro\n18.Adagio, ma non troppo e molto espressivo [Beethoven''s String Quartet #14 In C-Sharp Minor, OP.131]\n19.Allegro molto vivace [Beethoven''s String Quartet #14 In C-Sharp Minor, OP.131]\n20.Allegro moderato [Beethoven''s String Quartet #14 In C-Sharp Minor, OP.131]\n21.Andante, ma non troppo e molto cantabile [Beethoven''s String Quartet #14 In C-Sharp Minor, OP.131]\n22.Presto [Beethoven''s String Quartet #14 In C-Sharp Minor, OP.131]\n23.Adagio, quasi un poco andante [Beethoven''s String Quartet #14 In C-Sharp Minor, OP.131]\n24.Allegro [Beethoven''s String Quartet #14 In C-Sharp Minor, OP.131]\n', '2013-04-02 00:00:00', 375, 1, 16, '', '', 0, '', 1, 0, '2013-04-01 17:01:10', '2015-02-16 15:48:51', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
